subproject.description:
Support capacity development including institution and system development of regional and local governments through the integration of a set of focused initiatives, including:
1.Local government capacity development at bureau (regional) and woreda (district) levels;
2.Local development funding for basic infrastructure and services at woreda level (UNCDF);
3.Local Economic Development (LED) from both the public investment and inclusive financing perspectives;
4.Documentation of Lessons Learned and Best Practices

